metadata.name: Magic of fall # 1
metadata.description:
Fall is the season of soul. Its favorite time of the year. Weather is changing and every one love the colors of leaves, crisp air, pumpkin patches and enjoying beautiful scenery around them.  
 This change inspired me to venture out into the wilds and capture the beauty of nature in the camera 
These photos were taken in the Gran Sasso and Monti Della Laga national park Italy in 2017 during my visit in October about five years ago. It is a large aera ranging from Mediterranean to Euro-Siberian. It has a vibrant nature on the trail of ancient villages, archaeological sites, castles and abbeys, along prairies, plateaus, these are the experiences that you can enjoy through the park.
